Yahoo URL for Indian stocks in JSON format:

Where NAME is the scrip name (SUZLON, or RECLTD) and XC is a two letter 
exchange code - BO for BSE (bombay) and NS for NSE

http://finance.yahoo.com/webservice/v1/symbols/NAME.XC/quote?format=json
http://finance.yahoo.com/webservice/v1/symbols/NAME.XC/quote?format=xml
